This template can be used to cite all versions of the [[IUCN]] [[IUCN Red List|Red List of Threatened Species]]. A [http://www.iucnredlist.org/documents/redlist_website_users_guide.pdf user's guide] and [http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k2LnoLD2ss0 video] are available.

The search engine is [http://www.iucnredlist.org/apps/redlist/search here].

== Usage ==

=== Parameters ===

{| class="wikitable" style="font-size:90%; margin:auto; float:left;"
! Parameter
! Description
! Example
|-
| {{nbsp}}'''id'''
| The internal redlist id number.
| In http://www.iucnredlist.org/apps/redlist/details/149100/0, the id is 149100.
|-
| {{nbsp}}'''taxon'''
| The scientific name
| ''Passer domesticus''
|-
| {{nbsp}}'''assessors'''
| The person or group who assessed the status of the species, if specified
| BirdLife International
|-
| {{nbsp}}'''assessment_year'''{{nbsp}}
| The year the assessor evaluated the species.
| 2009
|-
| {{nbsp}}'''version'''
| The version of the list
| 2010.2
|-
| {{nbsp}}'''accessdate'''
| The date you downloaded the data
| 22 July 2010
|}
{{clear}}

<tt>accessdate</tt> and <tt>assessors<tt> are optional.

